                <h2>Turning Waste into Wonders</h2>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-2 my-2 border-top border-success"></div>
                <p>Welcome to our platform, a one-of-a-kind marketplace dedicated to transforming waste into valuable, artistic creations. We believe in the power of upcycling to reduce environmental impact, support creativity, and build a sustainable future. Our mission is simple yet profound: to redefine waste as a resource and connect eco-conscious insectioniduals with exceptional art.
                </p>
                <br>
                <!-- Our Story -->
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-2 my-2 border-top border-success" id="story-line"></div>
                <p>Our journey began with a shared passion for sustainability and creativity. Every year, households and industries generate vast amounts of waste, much of which ends up in landfills, harming the environment. We saw an opportunity to not only reduce waste but also empower artists and innovators to turn these discarded materials into beautiful and functional products.
                Thus, our platform was born—a place where waste finds new life, and people find inspiration.</p>
                <br>
                <!-- What We Offer -->
                <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-2 my-2 border-top border-success" id="offer-line"></div>
