                    <li><strong>Eco-Friendly Marketplace:</strong> A vibrant hub for buying, selling, and manufacturing art crafted from recycled materials.</li>
                    <br>
                    <li><strong>Community of Creators:</strong> A supportive space for artisans, designers, and manufacturers to showcase their creativity and earn a living sustainably.</li>
                    <br>
                    <li><strong>Sustainability Impact:</strong> We track and measure how every product sold contributes to reducing waste and conserving natural resources.</li>
                </ol>
                <br>
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-2 my-2 border-top border-success" id="mission-line"></div>
                <p>To create a world where waste is no longer a problem but a solution. By connecting people to sustainable art and practices, we aim to foster a culture of eco-conscious living and creativity.</p>
                <br>
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-2 my-2 border-top border-success" id="vision-line"></div>
                <p>To become the leading global platform for upcycled art, inspiring millions to make sustainable choices and reduce their carbon footprint.</p>
                <br>
                <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-2 my-2 border-top border-success" id="choose-line"></div>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Unique Products:</strong> Explore a diverse range of one-of-a-kind creations made from household and industrial waste.</li>
                    <br>
                    <li><strong>Support for Sustainability:</strong> Every purchase supports eco-friendly practices and a cleaner planet.</li>
                    <br>
                    <li><strong>Empowering Artists:</strong> We give artisans a platform to showcase their skills and grow their businesses.</li>
                </ol>
                <br>
                <h2>Join Our Movement</h2>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-2 my-2 border-top border-success" id="movement-line"></div>
                <p>By being part of our community, you’re not just buying or selling art—you’re contributing to a larger mission of sustainability and creativity. Together, we can make a difference, one upcycled product at a time.</p>
